                Absucus Ad<lb break="no" n="2"/>namonis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LX <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Nertomarus <lb n="5"/>et Locco Ate<lb break="no" n="6"/>dunus <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilii</ex></expan> et he<lb break="no" n="7"/>redes <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>itulum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>emoriae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in Wiederverwendung für ein Grab. Oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes ein Eichenkranz und Rosetten.</p>
            </div>
